title: TV Tonight: 'Walking Dead' -- who will survive zombie horde?
text:
TV Tonight: 'Walking Dead' -- who will survive zombie horde? By Chuck Barney Posted: 10/25/2015 03:00:00 AM PDT Andrew Lincoln as Rick Grimes on "The Walking Dead" on Oct. 25, 2015. (Gene Page/AMC) WATCH THIS: 
"The Simpsons" (8 p.m., Fox): In annual "Treehouse of Horror" episode, Kelsey Grammer reprises his role as Sideshow Bob, who finally kills Bart. Of course, zombies are supercool these days, so Bart is reanimated. 
"The Walking Dead" (9 p.m., AMC): Thanks to that blaring horn, a humongous zombie horde appears to be heading straight for Alexandria. Rick better have a good alternative plan -- and another motivational speech -- if we're going to get through this. (Hint: Not everyone does). 
"Halloween Wars" (9 p.m., Food Network): In the season finale, the remaining two teams create scream-worthy displays with an undead dinner party theme. Elvira helps to determine the winner. Sideshow Bob finally kills Bart only to reanimate him in the 'Treehouse of Horror XXVI' episode of 'The Simpsons.' (FOX)
